{
  "_doc": [
    "Per-room (per-SCENE) access logic. A scene under `scenes` is AUTHORED: it",
    "gets EXACTLY its `from` edges and its default (zone-gated) edge is dropped.",
    "Author zone-by-zone; every location-bearing scene in a zone must be",
    "reachable through authored edges before that zone is considered done.",
    "`from`: list of [source, requirement]. source = scene id (S_xxxx) or a zone",
    "name (zone-region entry). requirement = list ANDed; a nested list = OR-group;",
    "names match items.json. Items named here are auto-promoted to progression.",
    "`locations`: per-location region override (location name -> scene/zone) for",
    "chests/drops physically reached from a different room than their script",
    "scene. See data/room_graph_notes.md for the mapping rationale.",
    "",
    "coarse zone-medallion default until mapped.",
    "STATUS: ALL 6 zones authored (Hugo) — Wailing Blue (live-mapped) + Flooded",
    "Prison, Flames of Guilt, Silent Sands(+Rado), Corrupted Blood, Demonic Core",
    "(from the fan maps + Hugo walkthrough + location data). Key ability gates:",
    "wind, Dash(Silver Bracelet), Water Dragon Scales, Thunder(Levinstrike",
    "Warhammer), Fire(Crimson Lotusblade), climb(Earth Dragon Claws), Gold",
    "Bracelet; plus the per-zone keys + boss medallions. Verified 10/10 AP seeds",
    "beatable, 152/152 regions reachable, 6-sphere playthrough. CAVEAT: zones 3-6",
    "intra-floor topology + some Rado/mirror-maze adjacency are best-effort drafts",
    "(see room_graph_notes.md / git log); gates are anchored to item locations and",
    "beatability is verified, but a live pass could refine exact free-room edges."
  ],
